# KNOWLEDGE.md — Shared Team Knowledge Base

> **What this is:** Curated reference of facts, entities, and project state that all agents need to know. Maintained by the HUMAN team owner.
>
> **Who writes:** Human only. Agents read; agents do NOT modify.
>
> **Who reads:** All agents at every wake.
>
> **How it relates to MEMORY.md:** `MEMORY.md` is the firehose (every event). `KNOWLEDGE.md` is the distilled reference (what's true now). Weekly, the human moves stable facts from MEMORY → KNOWLEDGE.

